rows.label: tlk41700151_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Have you ever gone down
below this Alba Margen?

rows.label: tlk41700151_01_msg0002
rows.name:
You can only go when the
Cloud Sea is low.

rows.label: tlk41700151_01_msg0003
rows.name:
When you live on the surface of a Divine Beast,
like in Gula or Superbia, you're directly
affected by the Cloud Sea, right?

rows.label: tlk41700151_01_msg0004
rows.name:
That's why most cities are built on high ground
where the effects are less severe.

rows.label: tlk41700151_01_msg0005
rows.name:
I do envy places like Avaritia, which floats
on the Cloud Sea, or Invidia, where the city is
inside the Divine Beast.
